twiggs agreed to drop any custody claim of kimberly if tests 
revealed she was their daughter 
robert and barbara mays biological daughter arlena who was 
raised by the twiggs died in 1988 at the age of 9 of a congenital 
heart defect barbara mays died of cancer in 1981 
theres been virtually no discussion none whatsoever about 
the twiggs with me since the day after the blood tests came back 
