delighted the strike has been settled let me say that there is no 
threat to the pensions of the 125000 retirees across the country 
usery was named mediator by mrs dole in october after she 
visited striking workers in the coal fields of southern virginia 
strikers occupied a pittston processing plant in carbo va for 
several days in september and mines were blocked elsewhere more 
than 2000 strikers were arrested in the first three months of the 
walkout many for sitdown demonstrations and some for rock 
throwing three union officials were jailed 
